<TEXT>
   Former President Reagan and his wife, Nancy,
planned a quiet dinner at their Bel-Air home today to celebrate
their 37th wedding anniversary, spokesman Mark Weinberg said.
   On March 4, 1952, then-actor Ronald Reagan married actress Nancy
Davis in the Little Brown Church in Studio City, a Christian chapel
that continues to perform wedding ceremonies.
