<HEAD>Ten Killed When Explosion Rips Through Bus</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BEIJING (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Ten people were killed and 35 others were injured
when an explosion destroyed a passenger bus in the central city of
Zhengzhou, an official daily said Saturday.
   The Legal News said the explosion occurred on the bus shortly
after it left a Zhengzhou station Thursday.
